        <p class="faq-answer">Petsit Bend was established in 2014 by Abel Trotter during his sophmore year of college. Dedicated to giving pet owners peace of mind while away on their travels, Petsit Bend offers various petsitting services in the Bend area.</p>
        <p class="faq-answer">Abel has worked in the animal care field for a number of years, both as a dog daycare manager and as a vet assistant. He has experience working with canines, felines, horses, birds, and exotic pets, and is also Pet First Aid Certified by the American Red Cross.</p>
        <p class="faq-answer">Having established a number of regular clients and repeat customers through positive referrals and testimonials, Abel's goal is to continue to make connections and meet new clientele while studying Computer Science at OSU. An avid hiker, camper, gamer, and musician, you can often find Abel exploring one of Bend's many trails. When he isn't sitting behind his computer growling at code, he enjoys drinking local brews and listening to live music.</p>
